FrameUI 1.0.0 API

FrameUI is a Minecraft plugin library designed to easily create screens within a server.

A screen is composed of multiple item frames, each displaying a custom image, collectively forming a larger cohesive image. They support click and scroll interactions, allowing fo dynamic player interactions.
